{"type":"message","id":"aaa1bd0d","parentId":"d1b03649","timestamp":"2026-06-24T10:05:03.501Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking how the system works - is it fully automatic or does it need input? They want to understand the workflow without making changes.\n\nLet me explain the full flow based and the pipeline architecture.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nYes, **fully automatic** — once a project is added.\n\n## The Flow (24/7)\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ 1. DAEMON RUNS 24/7 (nexus_daemon.py)                       │\n│    ↓                                                         │\n│ 2. Scans whitelisted sites one-by-one (air-gapped 60s)      │\n│    ↓                                                         │\n│ 3. Scores each result against project niche (deterministic) │\n│    ↓                                                         │\n│ 4. Top leads → cheap-LLM quality gate (threshold 6.0)       │\n│    ↓                                                         │\n│ 5. Passed leads → bl-content agent writes article           │\n│    ↓                                                         │\n│ 6. Card sent to Telegram group                              │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n## What Needs Human Input?\n\n| Action | Frequency | Who |\n|--------|-----------|-----|\n| **Add project** | Once per project | You |\n| **Add source sites** | Optional, can be auto-seeded | You (or daemon) |\n| **Editorial feedback** | On each card (APPROVE/EDIT/REJECT) | You |\n| **Edit content** | Optional | You |\n\n## What Is Automatic\n\n- Scanning sites ✅\n- Scoring leads ✅\n- Quality gate ✅\n- Writing content ✅\n- Sending cards ✅\n\n---\n\n**Bottom line:** You only need to add projects and optionally respond to cards. Everything else runs itself. The daemon never stops — even now it's scanning sites for coinography.com."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"local-bifrost","model":"minimax.minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":18657,"output":370,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19027,"cost":{"input":0.0055971,"output":0.000444,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0060411}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782295492563,"responseId":"dd62b097-484b-4896-99db-d541d764d9e4"}}
